CREATE PROC [dbo].[ImportDimRatings] AS begin
INSERT INTO dbo.DimRatings
(
    MovieRatingDescription
)
SELECT * FROM (  
    SELECT
        DISTINCT Rating = 
        CASE Rating 
            WHEN 'PG=13' THEN 'PG-13'
            ELSE Rating
        END
    FROM
        extern.[catalog]
) cleaned_table
WHERE cleaned_table.Rating NOT IN (SELECT MovieRatingDescription FROM [dbo].[DimRatings])
;
END
GO
